title: Taking Charge - The Johnson White House Tapes 1963-64
description:
TAKING CHARGE - The Johnson White House Tapes 1963-64
Edited with commentary by Michael Beschloss

Simon & Schuster Audio
4 cassettes - 6 hours and 9 minutes running time.

MP3 128 kbps - mono

Authentic audio recordings made by Lyndon Johnson as President in the course of his duties. Fascinating.

According to the publisher, this is Part 1 of a projected trilogy, but since 1997 only a second volume, Reaching for Glory 1964-65, has been released.
